A professional, 3D-styled Tic-Tac-Toe game featuring a lush forest theme, flower-based game pieces, and an unbeatable AI opponent.

## ğŸ“ Abstract
Forest Fun Tic-Tac-Toe is a web-based strategy game designed to offer a visually immersive experience for both children and adults. Moving away from the traditional "pencil and paper" look, this project utilizes CSS3 3D transforms and glassmorphism to create a tactile, wooden UI. The core engine is powered by the **Minimax Algorithm**, ensuring a challenging experience where the AI never loses.

